  * Make sure `scope_exit` never throws on teardown. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

  * Restructure fold expression for Coverity. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

  * Prevent unneeded copies. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

