    so it is properly integrated.

    - introduce a standalone enum `attribute::Kind` outside of the
      `Attribute` class
    - use enum helpers for conversion from and to string

    Closes #1936.

1.13.0-dev.43 | 2025-01-08 09:39:45 +0100

