  * Decrease excessive RAM on some CI platforms. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

  * Make all CI tasks greedy. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

  * Rerun BTest up to three times in CI. (Benjamin Bannier, Corelight)

